verbose_text: Choi et al reported that the synthetic peptide (SP) ALEGGKSSGGGEATRDPEPT, which is present at the N-terminus of mature P. yezoensis protein 1 (PYP1), demonstrated chemoprotective effects against APAP induced Chang liver cell death.
